{"tid":1060483,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"香港xPOKERx八卦野","createTime":"2019-03-13T19:55:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T16:33:13.000Z","uid":181628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b3db47658a72badf757cced18262dda18c7df07a","tid":1060483,"uid":181628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T19:55:32.000Z","msg":"話說 上個月係旺角d私竇玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n突然有一班凶神惡煞沖入黎掃曬d碼落地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我果陣輸緊錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後佢地話果晚唔計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後大家拎返現金走（見到有人閪哂面）<br />\n不過因為沖入黎班人太恐怖 大家都無出聲好快走左<br />\n然後落到樓下 同朋友去食個麵<br />\n大約過左半個鐘 又見到班人走上去 <br />\n有制服 有幾個似係便衣 前後腳上左去<br />\n嚇撚到我瀨屎 如果真係在場玩緊會點？<br />\n<br />\n然後到而家都唔敢去呢d現金局私竇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好撚驚死 不過聽講<br />\n如果係香港Tourney 模式就唔算非法 <br />\n但係只知道hkppa有 $300 買入 $0獎池 純粹過手癮 <br />\n但係的士來回 比入場費 贏左$1都無真心無癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋pudong 不過蒲東最近爆左單野<br />\n腦細襯個客去廁所 偷個客籌碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 痴撚線<br />\n<br />\n網上其實我仲有玩過一隻叫 部落先鋒<br />\n其實都幾好玩 只不過每次都要打好耐<br />\n同埋計人民幣 入錢出錢有d煩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔想去澳門 但又想打poker 可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d79004d418dca1673a4ad3fb1909822913d64cf8","tid":1060483,"uid":181628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T00:04:47.000Z","msg":"香港其實有無線下錦標賽 或者SNG 要有獎金既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"806e580bdd981901b6bcba4d2e47c58e18e1dfb7","tid":1060483,"uid":22839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3db47658a72badf757cce